4️⃣ MAVEN (Build Tool)

Maven does:
	•	Download dependencies
	•	Build project
	•	Run project

You define dependencies in:

pom.xml

Example :

<dependency>
    <groupId>org.springframework.boot</groupId>
    <artifactId>spring-boot-starter-web</artifactId>
</dependency>

Then Maven downloads everything.


Important commands:

mvn clean install
mvn spring-boot:run

That’s all you need now.